{"type": "article", "id": 27236, "title": "汽水包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-24T06:49:07Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 55, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702130801niM8q4UI0T6JVyxA.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>一到夏天，汽水总是必不可少的消暑饮料。由于越来越多的人开始注意健康，<a href=\"http://thecreativemethod.com/\">The Creative Method</a> 为 Obi 的益生菌汽水设计包装时选择强调“有益的气泡”这一概念。每款汽水都根据不同的风味印有由大小不一的气泡组成的水果，表现出了汽水清新的口感。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130800BbyJa09jm2fEvHGV.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130800zC5mOkRxEIW6rtV2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.145\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130801CWIx3juZBe6GA7sP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.145\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}